quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Mohla ketsahalo e phethahalang –
  56,2,Nakong eo ha ho moea o tla thetseha ka ho tla ha eona
  56,3,E tla nyenyefatsa ba bang; ba bang e tla ba phahamisa
  56,4,Mohla lefats’e le tsukutlehang botebong ba lona
  56,5,Lithaba li tla batalla
  56,6,Hoo li tlang ho fetoha lerole
  56,7,Le tla hloptjhoa ka maquloana a mararo
  56,8,"Joale, sehlopha sa pele sa balekane ba letsohong le letona; – e be sehlopha seo etla be ele se joang"
  56,9,"E be sehlopha sa balekane ba letsoho le lets’ehali, ebe se ka letsohong le lets’ehali etlabe ele se joang"
  56,10,"Joale, ho latele sehlopha se ipabotseng, bao etla ba bona ba ipabotseng (Bophelong Bo-tlang)"
  56,11,Bao ke bona ba tla atamela haufinyane le Allah
  56,12,Kahar’a Lirapa tsa Nyakallo
  56,13,Ho tla be ho kopane mats’oele-ts’oele a batho ba khale-khale
  56,14,Le ba fokolang ba mengoaha ea morao-rao
  56,15,Ba tla be ba lutse holim’a Literone tse khabisitsoeng
  56,16,Le hona ho phomola ba shebane mahlong
  56,17,Ba tla be ba feptjoa ke bacha ho ea kahosafeleng
  56,18,Ka lijana le mepoptjoana e tletseng metsi a liliba tse kopotsang
  56,19,A ke keng a ba bakela ho opeloa ke hlooho le hona ho angoa ke botahoa
  56,20,Ba feptjoa le ka litholoana tseo ba li thabelang
  56,21,Le nama ea linonyana tseo ba li laba-labelang
  56,22,"Ho tla ba teng basali ba ratehang, ba bileng ba mahlo a ncho- cho"
  56,23,Ba joaloka mahakoe a patehileng kahar’a likhaketlana
  56,24,Tseo tsohle e le moputso oa tseo ba neng ba li etsa
  56,25,"Kamoo teng, ba ke ke ba utloa lipuo tse hlohlonts’ang litsebe le tsona lits’okelano"
  56,26,"Haese feela litumeliso tsa: “khotso! Khotso”"
  56,27,Sehlopha balekane ba letsoho le letona; ebe sehlopha seo e tla be e le se joang
  56,28,Se tla ba har’a lifate tsa leoka tse hlokang metsu
  56,29,Ba bile ba le har’a lifate tsa lipalesa tse ririellaneng
  56,30,Tse fanang ka moriti o pharaletseng
  56,31,Ba le har’a liliba tse kollang
  56,32,Le har’a litholoana ka mefuta
  56,33,"Tseo nako ea tsona e sa emiseng, kapa hona ho haneloa ka tsona"
  56,34,Ba tla be ba lutse holim’a mealo e phahamisitsoeng
  56,35,Hobane Ruri! Re ba hloletse balekane ba khethehileng
  56,36,Le hona ho ba etsa ba hloekileng
  56,37,"Ba ratehang, ba lilemong tse lekaneng"
  56,38,Molemong oa ba tla beng ba le ka letsohong le letona
  56,39,E tla be ele mats’oele-ts’oele a batho ba khale-khale
  56,40,Le mats’oele-ts’oele a mengoaha ea morao-rao
  56,41,"Joale, e be ho latela sehlopha se ka letsohong le lets’ehali: ebe sehlopha se ka letsohong le lets’ehali sona ke se joang"
  56,42,"Seo etla ba sehlopha se kahar’a phefo ea mocheso, le metsi a belang"
  56,43,Se bileng se leng kahar’a moriti oa Mosi o Mots’o
  56,44,"O sa pholang, kapa hona ho bata"
  56,45,"Hobane Pele ho mona, ba ne ba sitsitsoe ka nyakallo"
  56,46,Ba ile ba phehella ho kena sebeng se ts’abehang sa ho kopanya Allah le batlatsetsi
  56,47,"Ba ne ba tloaetse ho re: “Na ha re se re shoele re fetohile lerole le masapo, na ka nete re ka boela ra tsosoa hape"
  56,48,Le bo-ntat’a rona moholo?”
  56,49,"E re: “Ruri! batho ba khale-khale le ba mengoaha ea morao- rao"
  56,50,Ba tla khobokangoa ‘moho ts’episong ea letsatsi la pallo
  56,51,"Lona ba etsang bobe, ba bile ba nyefola Tsoho ea Bafu"
  56,52,Ruri! Le tla ja sefate se bitsoang Zaqqum
  56,53,Seo le tla tlatsa limpa ka sona
  56,54,Le tla noa metsi a belang kamora’o ho moo
  56,55,Le tla noa joaloka likamele tse nyoriloeng.”
  56,56,Sena e tla ba kamohelo ea bona ka Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  56,57,Ke Rona ba le hlotseng. Na le tla ke le amohele ‘nete
  56,58,Na le se le ile la bona lithere tsa lona
  56,59,"Ana ke lona ba li hlotseng, kapa ke Rona bahloli ba tsona"
  56,60,"Ke Rona ba faneng ka karolo ea lefu har’a lona, Re ke ke Ra sitoa"
  56,61,Hore Re fetolele libopeho tsa lona ho seo le sa se tsebeng
  56,62,"Ruri le tseba tlholeho ea mathomo. Joale, ke hobaneng ha le sa ketek lithoriso tsa Hae"
  56,63,Na le se le ile la bona peo eo le e jalang
  56,64,"Na ke lona ba e holisang, kapa ke Rona baholisi"
  56,65,"Hoja e bile Thato ea Rona, Ruri! Re ka be Re e ripitlile; le ne le ke ke la khaotsa ho lla ka hore"
  56,66,“Ruri! Re setse ka mejaro ea mekoloto holim’a ho se letho
  56,67,"Che, empa re buselitsoe morao!”"
  56,68,Na le bona metsi ao le’a noang
  56,69,"Na ke lona ba etsang hore a theohe marung, kapa ke Rona ba etsang hore a theohe marung"
  56,70,"Hoja e ne e le thato ea Rona, Re ne Re tla etsa hore a be bohla. Joale, hobaneng ha le sa fane ka liteboho"
  56,71,Na le se le ile la bona mollo oo le o besang
  56,72,"Na ke lona ba ileng ba melisa lifate lefats’eng, kapa ke Rona ba li melisang"
  56,73,"Etsoe Rona, ke Rona ba hlapants’itseng Qura’n e le sehopotso le khotsofalo molemong oa baahi ba lehoatateng le bohle lefats’eng"
  56,74,"Ka lebaka leo, u rorise lebitso la Mong`a hau, Ea Moholo- holo"
  56,75,"Che, ke bitsa bopaki ho likela ha Linaleli –"
  56,76,Seo ke kano e kholohali hoja ebe le ne le tsebile –
  56,77,Sena ke Qura‘n e hlomphehang ka ho fetisisa
  56,78,Ka har’a Lengolo le hlokometsoeng ka tieo
  56,79,"Eo ho seng mang, kapa mang ea ka e amang ntle le ba hloekileng"
  56,80,Ts’enolo e tsoang ho Mong`a Mafats’e
  56,81,Na ke Molaetsa oo le o nyefolang
  56,82,"Le entse tsela ea lona ea bophelo, ho e shanofatsa"
  56,83,"Joale, hobaneng nakong eo moea o nyolohelang ‘metsong oa motho ea shoang le sa thusetse"
  56,84,Empa ebile ka nako eo le ntse le shebile –
  56,85,"Empa Re le haufi haholo ho eena ho feta lona, empa le sa bone –"
  56,86,Hobaneng ha le sa ikamahanye le Rona
  56,87,Ha le busetse moea oo morao ha feela eba le buoa ‘nete
  56,88,"Joale, ke kahoo e reng haeba ele e mong oa ba haufinyane le Allah"
  56,89,"E be oa phela, a be a fumane khotsofalo le Serapa sa Nyakallo"
  56,90,Haeba e le e mong oa ba ka Letsohong le Letona
  56,91,"Joale, kemoo tumeliso ea ba ka letsohong le letona e tla ba: “Khotso e be le uena.”"
  56,92,"Empa haeba e le oa ba nyefoli, ba khelohileng"
  56,93,Kamohelo ea hae e tla ba ea metsi a belang
  56,94,Le hona ho cha Mollong oa Lihele
  56,95,Sena ke ‘nete ea sebele
  56,96,"Kahoo, u rorise lebitso la Mong`a hau, Ea Moholo-holo"